This is the code for the play button. 

using UnityEngine;
using UnityEngine.SceneManagement; 

public class Menu : MonoBehaviour
{
   public void PlayGame()
   {
    SceneManager.LoadSceneAsync("SampleScene");
   }
}

It creates a class called Menu. 
Inside that class there is a function called PlayGame.
Using Scenemanager to switch Scenes in the project. (Menu scene, Game scene)
When the play button is clicked, the function is called. 
